@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ksghmu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs((v0 * 0.05))
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.79 + tmp + 0.48) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.38)) * (0.26 + wp.cos(v0 + 0.32)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(v0) + wp.abs(0.78))
    data[tid] = v0
